metadata.description: Comprehensive motion-to-gait dictionary. Maps semantic motion concepts to neural network weight vectors for a 3-link PyBullet robot. Includes ALL viable synonyms — every trial that matched its concept criteria. Each entry cites the descriptive word, the LLM model, and the language.
metadata.robot: 3-link (Torso + BackLeg + FrontLeg), 2 hinge joints, 3 touch sensors, 2 motors

weight_keys.w03: torso touch → back leg motor (balance feedback)
weight_keys.w04: torso touch → front leg motor (balance feedback)
weight_keys.w13: back leg touch → back leg motor (local reflex)
weight_keys.w14: back leg touch → front leg motor (cross-coupling)
weight_keys.w23: front leg touch → back leg motor (cross-coupling)
weight_keys.w24: front leg touch → front leg motor (local reflex)

metadata.simulation: 4000 steps @ 240 Hz, MAX_FORCE=150N, headless PyBullet DIRECT mode
